{"id": "1512292099859546248", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "凸意識しないなら7凸24タイスが環境最強ですかね？火力と即効性がバカなので", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:08:53.635000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512293130475671622", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "859664949050998814", "author_name": "sr2uc", "author_bot": false, "content": "やっぱ24強いんですね。昨日使ってみて強いなって感じてたんで次の復刻で狙います！\n\nトゥルー　オルラ　ライカダフォダイル辺りってどんな評価されてますか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:12:59.353000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512293526837268510", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルー→深海に沈んだ…\nオルラ→最強サポーター\nライカー→バフの盛り方ヤバい、ついでにお前も火力出せるやん(3凸)\nダフォダイル→微妙", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:14:33.853000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512293612178768034", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "って感じですかね", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:14:54.200000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512293824930775160", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "859664949050998814", "author_name": "sr2uc", "author_bot": false, "content": "攻略サイト当てにならないんでめっっちゃ助かりますありがとうございますライカー24狙いにいきます", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:15:44.924000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512293859093254254", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォダイルはインフレに若干置いてかれてるだけで十分強いと思いますけどね〜\n無凸ダフォは無凸ライカーぐらいの強さだと思います", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:15:53.069000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512294700747591845", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "1コスでダメ強50%と軟化を付けれるだけでもサポーターとしては結構優秀だと思います｡\nまあ正直火力面は相当育成しないと､十分な出力出せませんが😢", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:19:13.735000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512294994394746921", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォあんま使ってないですけどあの1コスは強いですよね", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:20:23.746000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512295040951783525", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "やっぱり火力微妙か…", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:20:34.846000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512295461485023303", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォはつよいですよ", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:22:15.109000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512295690821439558", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "素の火力がそこまでないですが、刺突(不具合？)があるので", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:23:09.787000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512295972821143562", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "そうでした笑\n千変万化の2コスが謎に刺突判定持ってるので､反撃盛れるのも相まって､たまに敵にブッ刺さるんですよね笑", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:24:17.021000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:24:38.210000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512296056212291694", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "そんなのあるのか！？", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:24:36.903000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512296351424057425", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "融災だと､ランプシェードアイシャ第二形態突入時の無敵を無視して､1ターンキルしてる人とかいましたね笑", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:25:47.287000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Daffodil_Calm", "emoji_id": "1468259309052756182", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512296467442827264", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォ自身は結構強い\nただ今の環境は自前である程度狂気確保出来るキャラのが攻略楽なので、ちょっと劣って見える", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:26:14.948000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512296704937033768", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "てんとう虫みたいな超次元の遺物とか取れたら結構ダフォも暴れられる印象(個人的には)", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:27:11.571000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512297099906126057", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "今回の2波みたいにダフォがブッ刺さるってことが結構あって､汎用性が高いので一家に一ダフォは欲しいところさんですかね笑", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:28:45.739000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-05T03:28:57.750000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512312129321963700", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "自分今､サルバ,24が3凸で､タイスが7凸､\n他の限定は無凸で全員所持って感じなんですけど､\n次に3凸目指すとしたらどのキャラになりますかね？", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T04:28:29.031000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512323535446610012", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "超次元特有の空間に一度サッと湯通しする必要があるのと、後続のキャラが確定クリやらそもそも能力ｽｹでクリ率盛れたりと色々と便利すぎるのが良くないよね。", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T05:13:48.463000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512326040997859388", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "ﾀﾞﾌｫはキャラとの好感度上げからの恋愛まで発展させる古き良き恋愛シュミレーションゲームだけど、昨今のキャラは面倒くさがりなゆとり世代の為の即恋愛から始まって主人公と即繋がれる令和最新版仕様だから。", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T05:23:45.833000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-05T05:24:01.892000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512326807766962339", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "無難に次の新キャラ待ちで良さそうな気がする〜", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T05:26:48.645000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1126482815610011721"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1512312129321963700", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
